Code
-----
main.py - the game with the different states: menu, title, game
settings.py - custom additions to rabbyt
actions.py - stores inputted user actions
user_settings.py - object to store users controls
player.py - player module (the aircraft)
enemy.py - enemy base class, and all child enemy classes
chronos.py - chronal energy spark module
bullet.py - enemy and user bullets
layout.py - interprets text files to build layouts
tiles.py - makes scrolling background tile layouts
movement_pattern.py - movement patterns for enemies
wave.py - stores the starting xy coordinates, movement pattern, spawn time, and enemy types of a wave.
wave_element.py - stores xy coordinate, movement pattern, and type of each enemy in a wave
wave_handler.py -- handles the generation of enemy waves and parses level files.
healthbar.py - a simple health bar for the game
game_object.py - base class for objects in the level
state.py - base class for all game states

States
______
menu.py - area to choose next state
level.py - base class for creating levels
instructions.py - state for user to test movements
name.py - state for player to input name
highscores.py - highscore screen
cut[1-5].py - states for each of the cutscenes

Miscellaneous Files
-------------------
RabbitHighScores - high score file
